@startuml
title UML state machine diagram


state UserOps <<choice>>
state EndJoin <<choice>>

[*] --> ValidateUserType

state "validate the Type of User" as ValidateUserType
ValidateUserType : entry / select the user details
ValidateUserType : do / validate the registration details
ValidateUserType : exit / choose operations as registrar operations

state Registration
Registration : entry / fill the registration details
Registration : do / submit the registration details
Registration : exit / user is valid registration

state Login
Login : entry / fill the login details
Login : do / validate the login details
Login : exit / allow the user to login

state "Upload a Document" as UploadDocument
UploadDocument : entry / upload the document
UploadDocument : do / upload the document
UploadDocument : exit / upload another certificate / move to end

state "View Profile" as ViewProfile
ViewProfile : entry / view the citizen profile
ViewProfile : do / view the citizen profile
ViewProfile : exit / move to end

state "Apply for a Certificate" as ApplyCertificate
ApplyCertificate : entry / apply for a certificate with valid person
ApplyCertificate : do / send request to apply certificate
ApplyCertificate : exit / apply for another certificate / move to end

state "Certificate Sent to User" as CertSentUser
CertSentUser : entry / issue the certificate to user
CertSentUser : do / provide the certificate
CertSentUser : exit / update the citizen certificate in the citizen database

state "Registrar asks a Certificate for verification" as RegistrarAskCert
RegistrarAskCert : entry / registrar requests a certificate for verification
RegistrarAskCert : do / send request to the digitlocker
RegistrarAskCert : exit / request to digitlocker or receive the certificate provided by digitlocker or move to end

state "Digitlocker provides the Certificate" as DigitlockerCertificate
DigitlockerCertificate : entry / issue the certificate request
DigitlockerCertificate : do / fetch the required certificate from the citizen database
DigitlockerCertificate : exit / sent the provided certificate

ValidateUserType --> Registration : [Citizen Operation]
ValidateUserType --> RegistrarAskCert : [Registrar Operation]

Registration --> Login : [valid Registration]
Registration --> [*] : [Invalid Registration]

Login --> UserOps : [valid Login]
Login --> Login : [Invalid Login]

UserOps --> UploadDocument : [Uploading Documents]
UserOps --> ViewProfile : [Profile Viewing]
UserOps --> ApplyCertificate : [Applying for Certificate]

UploadDocument --> EndJoin : [Move to End]
UploadDocument --> UploadDocument : [Upload another document]
ViewProfile --> EndJoin : [Move to End]

ApplyCertificate --> ApplyCertificate : [Apply for another Certificate]
ApplyCertificate --> CertSentUser : [Send Request to Issuer]
ApplyCertificate --> EndJoin : [Move to End]

CertSentUser --> ApplyCertificate : [Issue the Applied Certificate]

RegistrarAskCert --> RegistrarAskCert : [Request for another Certificate]
RegistrarAskCert --> DigitlockerCertificate : [Send request to Digitlocker]
RegistrarAskCert --> EndJoin : [Move to End]

DigitlockerCertificate --> RegistrarAskCert : [Issue the Certificate for verification]

EndJoin --> [*]

@enduml